  "remarks": "\nYuri SHAMALOV is the President of Gazfond and he sits on the Board of Directors of Gazprombank SHAMALOV is therefore involved in work as a director or equivalent of entities (Gazfond and Gazprombank) in a sector (finance) of strategic significance to the Russian Government.\n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
